page.title: 03Food
page.content: For breakfast I normally have bacon and egg or cereals and for dinner I would have sandwiches in a school week whilst I would have a small cooked meal at the weekend.For tea, I would have lettuce, tomatoes, an egg hard boiled and some beef.For supper I would have some biscuits.That's what I have for the day. My parents own three food involved companies called {TERRY MOSS},{T and J {CATERING}, and{DUNELAW}.{TERRY MOSS}is the parent company of{T and J {CATERING}and{DUNELAW}.{TERRY MOSS} deals with eggs, egg packing and chickens and they are sold on the market stall or through the other two companies.{DUNELAW}owns a trailer registered as Crane Fraufehalf Moss special fast food stall with spit grills.By Neil Moss,aged 11.
